"NEWS GOV-MO: Seven Distinguished Individuals Conferred Honorary Doctoral Degrees by the University of Macau."
"The University of Macau held its "2021 Honorary and Higher Degree Conferral Ceremony" today, conferring Honorary Doctoral Degrees upon Zunyi Liu, Kaixian Chen, Xiuji Nakamura, Lanjuan Li, Liaoliang Li, Lilan Zhu, and Chaohui Jiang, in recognition of their outstanding achievements and significant contributions to the development of society and education."
